    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Demo内容：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包含第一章的主要剧情与挑战内容，但不包括多人联机模式与地图编辑器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《噗通世界：阿比亚的弹射之旅》主打爽快带感的平台跳跃玩法，还融入了末日题材的独特设定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身小型机器人阿比亚，你需通过跳跃、射击与快速反应在地下废墟中生存…… 甚至通关后还能亲手创建专属关卡内容。核心亮点如下：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>体验工具化精准射击+平台跳跃</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阿比亚周身的浮游炮本质是多功能工具。无论是触发机关开关、移动平台位置，还是借助勾爪攀升至高处，均需依靠它实现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩法核心为 “射击辅助平台跳跃”，全程无需对抗敌人，只需通过射击与跳跃的配合，即可找到突破障碍的巧妙解法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036850/extras/ec149eed127fd338878d4907fc81dc78.poster.avif?t=1772021500\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036850/extras/ec149eed127fd338878d4907fc81dc78.webm?t=1772021500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036850/extras/ec149eed127fd338878d4907fc81dc78.mp4?t=1772021500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>挑战硬核的快节奏反应</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏节奏对标《蔚蓝》的紧凑感：每一次跳跃需精准定位落点，每一次射击需把控时机。若不慎踩空平台，可回到检查点重新尝试；若一次性通关，则能收获 “完美通关” 的成就感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏难度偏高但机制公平，玩家的反应速度与操作精度才是通关的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036850/extras/9e791046f8c96cdd4ad40e12fbb744d7.poster.avif?t=1772021500\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036850/extras/9e791046f8c96cdd4ad40e12fbb744d7.webm?t=1772021500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036850/extras/9e791046f8c96cdd4ad40e12fbb744d7.mp4?t=1772021500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索修复末日地下废墟</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演机器人阿比亚，于地下废墟探索：包括坍塌的实验室、废弃工厂，以及藏有人类文明遗迹的隐秘角落。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在阴郁神秘的场景中，遍布各类隐藏线索。听从智脑的引导，不断探索，成为人类文明的拯救者吧.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036850/extras/47cad29284cbf3b9f13754c9b882b155.poster.avif?t=1772021500\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036850/extras/47cad29284cbf3b9f13754c9b882b155.webm?t=1772021500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036850/extras/47cad29284cbf3b9f13754c9b882b155.mp4?t=1772021500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>随心编辑属于你自己的关卡</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通关主线后仍有持续乐趣！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关卡编辑器支持玩家自由组合核心玩法元素：弹跳板、射击触发机关、限时速通挑战等，可根据喜好创建 “多人竞速派对” 的联机关卡，或设计 “高操作要求” 的速通挑战关卡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成创作后还能分享至社区，让其他玩家的操作精度接受考验或者与朋友分享你的创意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036850/extras/06d56784746f7a28c449ed71eec57cf2.poster.avif?t=1772021500\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036850/extras/06d56784746f7a28c449ed71eec57cf2.webm?t=1772021500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036850/extras/06d56784746f7a28c449ed71eec57cf2.mp4?t=1772021500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
